Class Soloist

  • java.lang.Object
    • symphony.domain.Person
      • symphony.domain.Soloist

  • public class Soloist
extends Person
    This class extends Person to create Soloist. Soloist adds a String to hold the expertise of this Soloist. It includes the getter and setter for expertise.
